{"tid":1457716,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機管局視乎恢復運作情況 明早6時實施航班重新編配","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:08:09.000Z","uid":34160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a985d0ff8d3b2d0c25d3d733fd0d373d49a397","tid":1457716,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"機管局表示，機場運作今日嚴重受阻，客機運作自下午約3時半後需全面取消。機管局會視乎機場運作的恢復情況，機管局與航空公司將由明日（13日）早上6時起實施航班重新編配，航班升降將會受到影響，呼籲旅客在出發前往機場前，先了解最新航班情況，亦需留意航空公司有關航班的最新消息，確認航班後才出發前往機場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190812&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59922119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190812%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59922119&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zmbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=5b5ccb69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190812%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59922119&h=f624032b\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190812&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59922119</a>"}]}